metrics_conclusion: So Long has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Melodic Complexity.
key_conclusion: So Long has sections analyzed in the following keys: D Major,  and G Major.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: Initially analyzed this in D, although it could be seen as V-IV-I movement in G with a short modulation to g minor before returning back to G major. It was quite clear by the end of the verse that the D was actually serving a dominant function rather than acting as the tonic, although it felt like the tonic during the beginning of the verse
